AjaxTask
========

AjaxTask is a Rails plugin that helps you manage running background tasks and returning a result to a user.

It is meant for running tasks that only take a short time < 30 seconds, but you don't want to block a request while the task is running.

Requirements:

JQuery 1.3+


Example
=======

Please see this link for a demo:

http://chrismoos.com/2010/02/09/ajaxtask-a-rails-plugin-for-managing-background-tasks/



